trans-unit.source: Represents a label in the instruction stream.
trans-unit.target: 表示指令流中的标签。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="Label" /> is used in conjunction with the <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.ILGenerator" /> class.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="Label" /> 与 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.ILGenerator" /> 类一起使用。

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the current instance is equal to a specified object.
trans-unit.target: 指示当前实例是否等于指定对象。

trans-unit.source: The object to compare with this <see langword="Label" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: 要与此 <see langword="Label" /> 实例进行比较的对象。

trans-unit.source: Checks if the given object is an instance of <see langword="Label" /> and is equal to this instance.
trans-unit.target: 检查给定对象是否为 <see langword="Label" /> 的实例和是否等于此实例。

trans-unit.source: Returns <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="obj" /> is an instance of <see langword="Label" /> and is equal to this object; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <paramref name="obj" /> 是 <see langword="Label" /> 的实例并等于此对象，则返回 <see langword="true" />；否则返回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" /> to compare to the current instance.
trans-unit.target: 要与当前实例进行比较的 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" />。

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the current instance is equal to the specified <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" />.
trans-unit.target: 指示当前实例是否等于指定的 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" />。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the value of <paramref name="obj" /> is equal to the value of the current instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <paramref name="obj" /> 的值等于当前实例的值，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Generates a hash code for this instance.
trans-unit.target: 生成此实例的哈希代码。

trans-unit.source: Returns a hash code for this instance.
trans-unit.target: 返回此实例的哈希代码。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" /> to compare to <c>b</c>.
trans-unit.target: 要与 <c>b</c> 进行比较的 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" /> to compare to <c>a</c>.
trans-unit.target: 要与 <c>a</c> 进行比较的 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" />。

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether two <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" /> structures are equal.
trans-unit.target: 指示两个 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" /> 结构是否相等。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="a" /> is equal to <paramref name="b" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see langword="true" /> 等于 <paramref name="a" />，则为 <paramref name="b" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.Label.Equals%28System.Reflection.Emit.Label%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 此运算符的等效方法是<xref:System.Reflection.Emit.Label.Equals%28System.Reflection.Emit.Label%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" /> to compare to <c>b</c>.
trans-unit.target: 要与 <c>b</c> 进行比较的 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" />。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" /> to compare to <c>a</c>.
trans-unit.target: 要与 <c>a</c> 进行比较的 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" />。

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether two <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" /> structures are not equal.
trans-unit.target: 指示两个 <see cref="T:System.Reflection.Emit.Label" /> 结构是否不相等。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="a" /> is not equal to <paramref name="b" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see langword="true" /> 不等于 <paramref name="a" />，则为 <paramref name="b" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The equivalent method for this operator is <xref:System.Reflection.Emit.Label.Equals%28System.Reflection.Emit.Label%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: 此运算符的等效方法是<xref:System.Reflection.Emit.Label.Equals%28System.Reflection.Emit.Label%29?displayProperty=nameWithType>。
